dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jordan Harris. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Jordan. My name is Teresa White.
Nice to meet you, Teresa. Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification?
Sure, my policy number is five six three two zero one.
Thank you, Teresa. I also need your date of birth to access your account securely.
My date of birth is the twenty-first of June, one nine eight seven.
Thank you for providing that information, Teresa. Is there anything specific you'd like to discuss today regarding your policy or any claims?
I need to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that, Teresa. Let's go ahead and get the details of the new vehicle.
Thank you for your time, Teresa. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
